    <h1>301 Redirect</h1>
    <p class="description">A permanent HTTP status code that tells browsers and search engines a page has moved. Passes <strong>90-99% of link equity</strong> to the new URL and is the SEO-safe way to move, merge, or retire pages.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
